item.description: The Motorola EM330 Titanium is an attractive flip-phone you’ll enjoy using. It has the standard two screens: a simple black and white exterior display for time, signal, battery, and other essentials, and a 1.8-inch color interior display. This AT&T flip-phone is more than basic. It boasts a 1.3-megapixel camera with 4x zoom and video recording, perfect for AT&T picture messaging. Its high-quality camera might even replace your regular digital camera. Don’t worry about storage space; a microSD card (up to 2GB) lets you capture countless memories.
